topic.title: MORE THAN THREE RECTAL WASHOUTS RECEIVED INDICATOR
topic.shortdesc: For the National Neonatal Data Set - Episodic and Daily Care, MORE THAN THREE RECTAL WASHOUTS RECEIVED INDICATOR indicates whether the baby had more than three rectal washouts on the NEONATAL CRITICAL CARE DAILY CARE DATE.
